									Our Premium Height Adjustable Desk is crafted with precision and care, featuring:
								</p>
								<ul class="p-t-20" style="list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 20px;">
									<li class="stext-102 cl6 p-b-10">Smooth electric height adjustment mechanism</li>
									<li class="stext-102 cl6 p-b-10">Premium quality desktop surface with scratch-resistant coating</li>
									<li class="stext-102 cl6 p-b-10">Sturdy steel frame with anti-collision technology</li>
									<li class="stext-102 cl6 p-b-10">Cable management system included</li>
									<li class="stext-102 cl6 p-b-10">Memory settings for your preferred heights</li>
									<li class="stext-102 cl6">5-year warranty on frame and motor</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
