												</div>

												<p class="stext-102 cl6">
													Excellent build quality and smooth height adjustment mechanism. The desk surface is spacious and the cable management system keeps everything tidy. Customer service was also very helpful during installation.
												</p>
											</div>
										</div>
										
										<!-- Review -->
										<div class="flex-w flex-t p-b-68">
											<div class="wrap-pic-s size-109 bor0 of-hidden m-r-18 m-t-6">
												<img src="images/avatar-02.jpg" alt="AVATAR">
											</div>

											<div class="size-207">
												<div class="flex-w flex-sb-m p-b-17">
													<span class="mtext-107 cl2 p-r-20">
														Rahul Kapoor
													</span>

													<span class="fs-18 cl11">
														<i class="zmdi zmdi-star"></i>
														<i class="zmdi zmdi-star"></i>
														<i class="zmdi zmdi-star"></i>
														<i class="zmdi zmdi-star"></i>
														<i class="zmdi zmdi-star"></i>
													</span>
												</div>

												<p class="stext-102 cl6">
													This desk has transformed my work-from-home setup. The height adjustment is whisper-quiet and the memory settings are a game-changer. Premium quality through and through.
												</p>
